{"tid":2094113,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"打通兩戶 密封通道  違規擴建無主寮屋 陶輝涉霸死人地","createTime":"2020-07-04T10:46:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T11:06:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c4b7250c07a8953e935166ec2e3550099b358c11","tid":2094113,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T10:46:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200704/ASIW2ZDXFAFFQ4DUBV56463QAQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200704%2FASIW2ZDXFAFFQ4DUBV56463QAQ%2F&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmpwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=2faed974\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200704%2FASIW2ZDXFAFFQ4DUBV56463QAQ%2F&h=09ba306b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200704/ASIW2ZDXFAFFQ4DUBV56463QAQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n打通兩戶 密封通道 <br />\n違規擴建無主寮屋 陶輝涉霸死人地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lZrQWmqp_UuzeFBJdMPcpt3bdu0=/1040x812/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QQL4FE7RVTFZSWB53XYHSAV65U.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FlZrQWmqp_UuzeFBJdMPcpt3bdu0%3D%2F1040x812%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQQL4FE7RVTFZSWB53XYHSAV65U.gif&h=d10d30ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警務處助理處長陶輝（Rupert Dover）及其警長妻子張雅詩居住的碧水新村1號牌照屋，除被揭僭建及霸佔官地外，更涉嫌霸佔毗鄰的3號屋。早前有消息指，3號屋持牌人已離世多年，質疑陶輝夫婦「生人霸死地」，地政總署昨日終於證實，3號屋的土地牌照持有人已身故，但寮屋仍發現有違規擴建情況，正調查是否有人未經批准轉讓牌照。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：申霸地規範化 楊祖賜劉肇邦暫免拆僭建<br />\n<br />\n據了解，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n意味兩屋曾被打通。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n地署︰正查是否未經批准轉讓<br />\n<br />\n自今年5月1日起，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n現正進行糾正工程。<br />\n<br />\n惟地政總署又指，上<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n採取適當跟進行動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JgGq1ErxrTcdwshnYvzuNymn7pc=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7S2CC65NTTA3VGPSWNRWXNZYSY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJgGq1ErxrTcdwshnYvzuNymn7pc%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7S2CC65NTTA3VGPSWNRWXNZYSY.jpg&h=989f6b5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陶輝的碧水新村1號屋涉僭建及霸佔毗鄰3號屋，工人進入兩屋相連通道處理清拆工程。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多番被投訴 署方懶理<br />\n<br />\n有知情人士透露，原有3號屋的持牌人已逝世多年，直斥地政總署不可能毫不知情，批評該署任由他人違規霸屋，「點會畀佢哋霸人哋間死人屋，有冇搞錯？」<br />\n<br />\n區議員及村民指，曾多次就3號屋向地政總署<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n佔，惟寮管處指寮管政策不並規管佔用人身份。<br />\n<br />\n地政總署2017年及2018年接獲兩宗<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n身為警務處助理處長的陶輝，4月被揭發違規居住清水灣碧水新村1號屋，該屋天台及花園更涉僭建及霸佔官地，近日才終陸續清拆僭建物。其警長妻子張雅詩，則於同村的61號屋無牌經營旅館，早前民政事務總署已確認61A號屋未領取旅館牌照，而地政總署則指該屋違反土地牌照及寮屋規定，已發信要求限期前糾正。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0y8506RrYv74sjfoglOENVpy_kI=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ENHKIQPOK2BTTWFFLQJYDAFK2Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0y8506RrYv74sjfoglOENVpy_kI%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FENHKIQPOK2BTTWFFLQJYDAFK2Q.jpg&h=2539e662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陶輝"},{"pid":"05d6bda8ac28d31ec26b392691d37caa02afecd6","tid":2094113,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T11:00:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3號屋的持牌人已逝世多年</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n死因係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a50486f05dda5618f9a8b32aea5c9b19938d5b","tid":2094113,"uid":118553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T11:02:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b32dbf0a625d127dd5e34f524a7ad1d94a79855b","tid":2094113,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05d6bda8ac28d31ec26b392691d37caa02afecd6","tid":2094113,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T11:00:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3號屋的持牌人已逝世多年</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n死因係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T11:03:46.000Z","msg":"參與非法集結定無行返上行人路??<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7447da933a91461e5c8fee1f94483f9ce9fe28d","tid":2094113,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05d6bda8ac28d31ec26b392691d37caa02afecd6","tid":2094113,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T11:00:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3號屋的持牌人已逝世多年</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n死因係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T11:04:32.000Z","msg":"無可疑嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bba4f6cbee96ee5ed5d65c25c2413b395b110df8","tid":2094113,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T11:06:00.000Z","msg":"哦, 你爆黑警大鑊, 分裂國家"}]}